nzertsaal und die Bibliothek in Espoo, gehören zu den Realisierungen des Büros, wie auch gar städtebauliche, so etwa der Masterplan für die Umgestaltung des ehemaligen Areals des Flughafens von Oslo.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecturezFinlandy20th centuryvCatalogs. 0aArchitecturezFinlandy20th century. 0aArchitecturezFinlandy21st centuryvCatalogs. 0aArchitecturezFinlandy21st century. 4aArchitektur. 4aFinnland. 4aHolz. 4aNachhaltigkeit. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh1 aDavey, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNikula, Riitta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062112908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303461147340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783034611473423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783034611473/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-062112-9  DGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014